vdaQdReports.name: Test
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT ALIAS.ALIAS, ALIAS_PERMISSIONS.APPLICATION_NAME, ALIAS_PERMISSIONS.ID_PERMISSION FROM ALIAS, ALIAS_PERMISSIONS WHERE (ALIAS_PERMISSIONS.ALIAS = ALIAS.ALIAS) AND (ALIAS_PERMISSIONS.APPLICATION_NAME ='MEP')

vdaQdReports.name: Interbanking
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT ALIAS_PROFILES.ALIAS, ALIAS_PROFILES.APPLICATION_NAME, ALIAS_PROFILES.DATA_VALUE1, ALIAS_PROFILES.DATA_VALUE2, ALIAS_PROFILES.DATA_VALUE3, ALIAS_PROFILES.DATA_VALUE4 FROM ALIAS_PROFILES WHERE (ALIAS_PROFILES.APPLICATION_NAME LIKE'VISA%O%' AND ALIAS_PROFILES.ALIAS ='BMN95432' OR ALIAS_PROFILES.ALIAS ='PNV68152')

vdaQdReports.name: TraduccionMastercard
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT PROFILE_TRANSLATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME, PROFILE_TRANSLATIONS.DATA_VALUE1, PROFILE_TRANSLATIONS.DATA_VALUE2, PROFILE_TRANSLATIONS.TRANSLATION_NAME, PROFILE_TRANSLATIONS.TRANSLATION_VALUE FROM PROFILE_TRANSLATIONS WHERE (PROFILE_TRANSLATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME ='VISA_ONLINE' OR PROFILE_TRANSLATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME LIKE'Master%')

vdaQdReports.name: FallasEnEjecuciones
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME, APPLICATIONS.CONNECTOR_NAME, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_RESULT, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_START_TIME, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_FINISH_TIME, CONNECTORS.CONNECTOR_TYPE FROM APPLICATIONS, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT, CONNECTORS, SCHEDULER_TASK WHERE (SCHEDULER_TASK.TASK_NAME = SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_NAME AND SCHEDULER_TASK.APPLICATION_NAME = APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME AND APPLICATIONS.CONNECTOR_NAME = CONNECTORS.NAME) AND (SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_RESULT ='FAILURE' AND APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_STATUS ='ACTIVE')

vdaQdReports.name: FallasEnEjecucionUltmas24Horas
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME, APPLICATIONS.CONNECTOR_NAME, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_RESULT, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_START_TIME, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_FINISH_TIME, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_COMMENT, CONNECTORS.CONNECTOR_TYPE FROM APPLICATIONS, SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT, CONNECTORS, SCHEDULER_TASK WHERE (SCHEDULER_TASK.TASK_NAME = SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_NAME AND SCHEDULER_TASK.APPLICATION_NAME = APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME AND APPLICATIONS.CONNECTOR_NAME = CONNECTORS.NAME) AND (SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_RESULT ='FAILURE' AND APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_STATUS ='ACTIVE') AND (days(SCHEDULER_TASK_RESULT.TASK_FINISH_TIME) = days (current date)-1 )

vdaQdReports.name: Alias Mastercard
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT ALIAS.ALIAS, ALIAS.ALIAS_STATUS, ALIAS.APPLICATION_NAME, ALIAS.USER_IDM FROM ALIAS WHERE (ALIAS.APPLICATION_NAME LIKE'Mastercard%' AND ALIAS.ALIAS_STATUS ='ACTIVE')

vdaQdReports.name: Usuarios Administrados por VDA
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT USERS.ADMINISTRADO_VDA, USERS.CENTRO_COSTOS, USERS.FULLNAME, USERS.LAST_UPDATE, USERS.SUPERVISOR_USER_ID, USERS.TYPE, USERS.USER_IDM, USERS.USER_STATUS FROM USERS WHERE (USERS.ADMINISTRADO_VDA ='Y')

vdaQdReports.name: Alias Pendientes de Asociacion
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT ALIAS.ALIAS, ALIAS.ALIAS_STATUS, ALIAS.APPLICATION_NAME, ALIAS.ASSOCIATED, ALIAS.DESCRIPTION, ALIAS.LAST_UPDATE, ALIAS.USER_IDM FROM ALIAS, APPLICATIONS WHERE (ALIAS.APPLICATION_NAME = APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME) AND (APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_STATUS ='ACTIVE' AND ALIAS.ASSOCIATED ='n')

vdaQdReports.name: Supervisor de un usuario
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT U.USER_IDM, U.SUPERVISOR_USER_ID, U2.FULLNAME FROM certific.USERS U INNER JOIN certific.USERS U2 ON U2.USER_IDM =  U.SUPERVISOR_USER_ID  WHERE (U.USER_IDM ='PRM65523')

vdaQdReports.name: Reporte para Tincho 2
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT ALIAS_PROFILES.ALIAS, ALIAS_PROFILES.APPLICATION_NAME, ALIAS_PROFILES.DATA_VALUE1, ALIAS_PROFILES.DATA_VALUE2, ALIAS_PROFILES.DATA_VALUE3, ALIAS_PROFILES.DATA_VALUE4, USERS.USER_IDM FROM ALIAS_PROFILES, USERS, APPLICATIONS, ALIAS WHERE (ALIAS_PROFILES.APPLICATION_NAME = APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME AND ALIAS.USER_IDM = USERS.USER_IDM AND ALIAS.ALIAS = ALIAS_PROFILES.ALIAS) AND (APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_STATUS ='ACTIVE' AND ALIAS.ALIAS_STATUS ='ACTIVE')

vdaQdReports.name: Listado de ejecuciones
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT SCHEDULER_TASK.APPLICATION_NAME, SCHEDULER_TASK.DAY_OF_MONTH, SCHEDULER_TASK.DAY_OF_WEEK, SCHEDULER_TASK.HOUR, SCHEDULER_TASK.MINUTES, SCHEDULER_TASK.MONTH, SCHEDULER_TASK.TASK_NAME, SCHEDULER_TASK.TASK_MODE FROM SCHEDULER_TASK, APPLICATIONS WHERE (APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME = SCHEDULER_TASK.APPLICATION_NAME) AND (APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_STATUS ='ACTIVE')

vdaQdReports.name: Listado de aplicaciones
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME, APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_STATUS, APPLICATIONS.CONNECTOR_ADDITIONAL_PARAMETER_1, APPLICATIONS.CONNECTOR_NAME, APPLICATIONS.DESCRIPTION, APPLICATIONS.LAST_UPDATE, APPLICATIONS.PERMISSIONDATA_NAME1, APPLICATIONS.PERMISSIONDATA_NAME2, APPLICATIONS.PERMISSIONDATA_NAME3, APPLICATIONS.PERMISSIONDATA_NAME4, APPLICATIONS.PROFILEDATA_NAME1, APPLICATIONS.PROFILEDATA_NAME2, APPLICATIONS.PROFILEDATA_NAME3, APPLICATIONS.PROFILEDATA_NAME4, APPLICATIONS.QUERY_PROFILES_PERMISSIONS, APPLICATIONS.QUERY_USER_PERMISSIONS, APPLICATIONS.QUERY_USER_PROFILES, APPLICATIONS.READING_MODE, APPLICATIONS.RUN_LIMIT, CONNECTORS.CONNECTOR_TYPE, CONNECTORS.DESCRIPTION, CONNECTORS.STATUS, CONNECTORS_PROPERTIES.KEY, CONNECTORS_PROPERTIES.VALUE FROM APPLICATIONS, CONNECTORS, CONNECTORS_PROPERTIES WHERE (CONNECTORS.NAME = CONNECTORS_PROPERTIES.NAME AND APPLICATIONS.CONNECTOR_NAME = CONNECTORS.NAME) AND (APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_STATUS ='ACTIVE' AND CONNECTORS.STATUS ='ENABLED')

vdaQdReports.name: AplicacionesEjecucionManual
vdaQdReports.sql: SELECT APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME, APPLICATIONS.DESCRIPTION, APPLICATIONS.LAST_UPDATE FROM APPLICATIONS, SCHEDULER_TASK WHERE (APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NAME = SCHEDULER_TASK.APPLICATION_NAME) AND (APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_STATUS ='ACTIVE' AND SCHEDULER_TASK.TASK_MODE ='MANUAL')

vdaQdReports.name: Logs
vdaQdReports.sql:
SELECT 
    L.LOG_DATE,
    L.LOG_TYPE,
    L.LOG_LEVEL,
    L.LOG_MESSAGE
FROM 
    certific.LOGS L
WHERE
    L.LOG_TYPE = 'erroresLogger'
    and year(L.LOG_DATE) = 2025
    and month(L.LOG_DATE) = 2
    and day(L.LOG_DATE) = 10
    and hour(L.LOG_DATE) = 14
    and minute(L.LOG_DATE)= 20
    and lower(L.LOG_MESSAGE) like '%deadlock%'
